title: Hour 1 -Draymond Green Isn't Great, LIV Tour
itunes:title: Hour 1 -Draymond Green Isn't Great, LIV Tour
description:
Dan doesn't think the Boston Celtics have any fear of a mediocre Draymond Green. And he addresses Rory McIlroy's stance on golfers deserting the PGA Tour for the LIV Tour just for the money.
